This is a comprehensive reform bill to ensure that the districts are fair and that all voters are heard.
My bill ends partisan gerrymandering nationwide, helps more people vote by making Election Day a holiday and creates open top-two primaries
The American people are deeply frustrated because they can see that Congress just doesn’t reflect the country’s priorities.
and that means a small and disproportionately partisan percentage of the population has an outsized influence on Congress
In too many districts, the only election that matters is the primary
Gerrymandering, low voter turnout and a broken primary system have  warped Congress and encouraged extreme partisanship
The Open Our Democracy Act has a very simple goal – to make the House of Representatives truly representative.
